{"tid":1360201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［我係鬼］解放軍未來我邀請","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:18:14.000Z","uid":18648,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43679b9e3a78e9bc1950756ca3777940f1b54d3c","tid":1360201,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"只要出解放軍 <br />\n話知佢有無開槍<br />\n話知佢有無打人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即走</span><br />\n<br />\n美國講明出解放軍鎮壓<br />\n會考慮取消香港關係法<br />\n再者<br />\n解放軍比班狗更無性<br />\n香港人就有籍口團結<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">武裝起義</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一取消同起義嘅話<br />\n只要有足夠抗暴政嘅民意<br />\n香港就有機會成立臨時政府<br />\n而推翻港共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有危先有機<br />\n距離香港獨立不遠了<br />\n<br />\n足弟手足<br />\n萬事小心<br />\n我地要有命見到香港重光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e456da85c869f8ced8ee1fd7e48a67c764fe09","tid":1360201,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:07:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522029cc35bd329f0ef3b5e4feede48579d68398","tid":1360201,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"86b0ee7c3dd41f7400165a445edc79b85f47ae67","tid":1360201,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:14:36.000Z","msg":"《極重要》727反三黑之 陣型 裝備 心態<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a4fd42b87b68623ff16ad57e6d1b86ebfbfea3e","tid":1360201,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:14:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"